## Quick start

```bash
pnpm install
bn dev
```

## Commands

- `bn dev` — local dev server (Wrangler Pages dev).
- `bn deploy --preview` — deploy to a preview URL.
- `bn deploy --prod` — deploy to production.
- `bn doctor` — verify local setup.

## Stack

- BaseNative runtime + router + server.
- Cloudflare Pages + Workers (via Wrangler).
- Shared `@basenative/eslint-config`, `@basenative/tsconfig`, `@basenative/wrangler-preset`.

